- Ensure all navigation in frontend templates uses `url_for()` with the actual page routes (e.g., `dashboard`, `book_catalog`, `book_details`, `my_borrowings`, `user_profile`), which is already done correctly.

This cleanup will ensure the backend routes correspond exactly to those used in the frontend, fulfilling regulation #4 and avoiding any potential routing confusion.

